{"tid":1402141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚有份屌前線既全部去面壁思過！","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:20:42.000Z","uid":108350,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de497404eef6181d470de5c693ec850a0b7773e6","tid":1402141,"uid":108350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"我想講<br />\n和理非走果陣前線有無走出黎屌臭你呀？<br />\n更何況呢度一大班冷氣軍師<br />\n想坐享其成，仲好意思出黎屌？<br />\n<br />\n你可以唔同意前線決定<br />\n你可以話佢地做錯決定<br />\n但你無資格屌<br />\n<br />\n未到兩個月<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係咪已經忘記不割𥱊，不督灰啦？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n連登巴絲請注意<br />\n任何互屌分化post請<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">立即負評<br />\n唔好回<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"546c994ec387fddf8d4d3fac75620031cbdea48f","tid":1402141,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c3037615cb4153aa2ab399799fe3b5ca47f5123d","tid":1402141,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"416bac7cc3029f93fff743b250557d433d7854b2","tid":1402141,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全部同我入去睇攻略備戰聽日港島西戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再作無謂犧牲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩火請睇#7職業同#9工具</span><br />\n<br />\n[致勝兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />nline攻略]大整合香城Online西區地圖使用各項優勢戰略(路線、反思、職業...)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1399804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h